== Instructions for release == 

* Update conf/iCubVersion.cmake

* Update yarp version info inside admin/scripts/current_dependencies.txt 

* Update licensing info
  Run ./admin/scripts/license.sh
  Check main/COPYING_new
  Check main/AUTHORS_new
  cp main/COPYING_new main/COPYING
  cp main/AUTHORS_new main/AUTHORS

* Update main/ChangeLog and ChangeLog with tag notice

* Make tag
  Commit new version, write down revision svn revision number (REVISION)
  
  svn copy -r REVISION https://robotcub.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/robotcub/trunk/iCub https://robotcub.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/robotcub/tags/iCub1.1.6

* Make packages

  ./admin/scripts/icub-package.sh 1.1.6

This will produce inside package-tmp:

  iCub-src-1.1.6.tar.gz
  iCub-src-1.1.6.zip

and will automatically upload them on eris

Update the packages to sourceforge:

  scp package-tmp/iCub-src-1.1.7.tar.gz USERNAME,robotcub@frs.sourceforge.net:/home/frs/project/r/ro/robotcub/main/iCub-1.1.7/iCub-src-1.1.7.tar.gz
  scp package-tmp/iCub-src-1.1.7.zip USERNAME,robotcub@frs.sourceforge.net:/home/frs/project/r/ro/robotcub/main/iCub-1.1.7/iCub-src-1.1.7.zip
  
  

